{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act46side", "eventName": "雪山降臨1101", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "OS-1", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "呼號聲中", "storyInfo": "諾希斯前往萊茵生命觀測站詢問天災成因，埃琳娜發現天災發生前的觀測記錄被刻意修改，研究員卡羅琳也下落不明。緊接著，憤怒的謝拉格民眾包圍了觀測站。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G3_rhineobservatory_i", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.7, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>謝拉格-萊茵生命觀測站</><p=2>兩個月前</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#7$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇……建得真快，這個規模的觀測站竟然在這麼短的時間內就蓋好了……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#7$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的工程規模，商務科這次恐怕要大失血了吧。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格觀測站的議案在委員會投票通過後的第一時間，就有兩位數的金融機構找上門了。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣看來，經費反而是這次計劃中最不需要擔心的部分。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫默，老實說……我本來以為這項提案在委員會那邊沒這麼容易通過呢。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我猶豫過，我還是堅持認為現在萊茵生命對於“星莢”的研究進度太過激進了，仍有許多潛在的問題我們尚未考慮周全。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我也意識到，或許我期待的那個穩定的局面永遠不會到來。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管任何時候，我們能相信的只能是具體的人。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我要感謝你的信任了，赫默委員。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望我們做的這一切，都是有價值的……", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然啦，對於整個萊茵生命來說，這個觀測站都是絕無僅有的機會吧。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了星莢的研究，謝拉格低源石濃度的環境也是很難得的生物研究場所。還有馬里亞姆！他也一直說早就想來喀蘭雪山看看了。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連斐爾迪南也是，拿到觀測站的立案通知後，只用了兩週的時間就交出了觀測站核心能量井的供能方案。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過之後他就又全心投入他的理論研究了，負責後續執行工作的是能量科的埃琳娜。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望在考察之外，和謝拉格方面的相處也可以順利……", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassdooropen"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想這一點就不勞各位學者操心了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "觀測站的大門從外側打開，來人掃去肩頭落下的雪花，走入室內。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又見面了，諾希斯先生。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "例行訪問，來確認觀測站的修建工作是否有需要幫助的地方……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過看起來，這裡的進度十分理想。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯抬起頭，萊茵生命觀測站光潔而寬闊的吊頂之上鑲嵌著散發柔光的燈帶。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵生命與喀蘭貿易合力，在短得不可思議的時間內搭建起了這座堅固又光亮的小殿堂。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外形特殊、前衛，和謝拉格的民宅相比如同來自未來的造物。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喀蘭貿易會盡一切可能協助萊茵生命推動觀測站的計劃，也願意在工作之外為各位提供必要的幫助。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要萊茵生命不違背條約中的共識，各位在謝拉格的活動就可以暢通無阻。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝您的好意，諾希斯先生。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵生命只是一個科學研究公司，除了研究以外不會有任何別的目的。我想我們沒有理由主動破壞條約。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……當然，我也是這樣相信的。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像這樣的跨國合作，在整個泰拉都沒有先例，這樣的初次嘗試必然會有重重阻礙……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想強調，只要我們雙方在研究資訊上保持必要的坦誠，類似特里蒙那樣的意外情況，完全可以避免。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1031_slent2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_1031_slent2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了！聖女大人會來觀測站參訪嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等觀測站正式落成的時候，聖女應該會出席相關的儀式……您想見聖女大人，是有什麼事嗎？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，沒有什麼嚴肅的理由啦，只是有點好奇。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得上次拜訪聖女大人的時候，她一開始還十分牴觸我們的合作計劃，但後來忽然就同意了。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有點好奇，她到底是因為什麼才轉變了想法，一直都想找個機會問問她呢。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女平日工作繁忙，如果您想和聖女交流的話，可以抽空去參與一下本地的儀式活動……如果您感興趣的話。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖女和蔓珠院的長老都很樂意招待各位……如果各位有這樣的打算，我會代為安排。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好周到，您真適合做這份工作呢~", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#10$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "基本的地主之誼，這是謝拉格應該做的。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位應該都會在謝拉格停留一段時間，我們都希望這是一段沒有麻煩……愉快的合作。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝您的體貼，如果沒有您的幫助，這次的合作很難進展得如此順利。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是幫助，是達成我們共同的目標，繆爾賽思小姐。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喀蘭貿易為你們連接謝拉格的山峰，鋪設方便前來的路與行動的自由。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照約定，萊茵生命會共享研究本地生態得出的部分資料，協助本土藥物研發。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，菲茨羅伊主任會針對合約的細節和喀蘭貿易詳談的。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是個研究員，沒那麼善於交際。只希望能讓您相信，萊茵生命是帶著絕對友善的態度來到這片神聖的土地的。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少在這一點上，我們應該沒有區別。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二人握手，相互點頭，臉上帶著笑，如同所有標題寫著“展開友好合作”的新聞照片一樣。"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必有太多擔憂……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#9$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要遵守契約，我們就仍是“朋友”。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g5_rhinelab_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜組長，喀蘭貿易的代表來了。", "name": "能量科研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們要求儘快與萊茵生命代表進行會面。", "name": "能量科研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？我們近期應該沒有與喀蘭貿易開會的安排吧？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是因為天災？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "能量科研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們希望能針對天災的成因和萊茵生命進行討論，至少希望我們可以提供觀測站的觀測資料。", "name": "能量科研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，你見到卡羅琳前輩了嗎？觀測資料應該是她在負責的吧？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是……另一個想找您確認的問題了。", "name": "能量科研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從昨天上午開始，我們就沒有人見到過她……", "name": "能量科研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2007_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G3_rhineobservatory_i", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然帶著侍衛包圍了觀測站，還要求所有研究員在大廳集合並接受“詢問”。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯先生，這就是喀蘭貿易對待朋友的態度嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寬敞的前廳之中，研究員們三三兩兩地站成一片，集中在廳堂內側。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一頭，諾希斯帶著希瓦艾什家的侍衛占據了靠近大門的外側空間。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩群人之間自然而然地割裂出一道界限，如同被河流分割的兩片土地。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是“請求”，而非“要求”……至少從結果來看，並不是所有研究員都在這裡。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白，諾希斯先生，您要找的是哪一位研究員？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位之前被發現，出現在謝拉格軍事禁區的研究員。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯的視線掃過研究員們，一個一個確認著他們的面目。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高大的侍衛沉默不語，研究員們無聲地相互交換眼神。"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但是她現在並不在這裡。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看樣子，萊茵生命並沒有辦法完全掌握每一位研究員的行蹤。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "諾希斯先生，如果您是在懷疑萊茵生命內部存在某種間諜行為，我們希望您可以透過正式的流程提出指控。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像今天這種突發的狀況，請恕我們沒有辦法配合您的調查。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#11$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然……我今天來這裡，還為另外一件事。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信各位已經有所聽聞，幾個小時前，謝拉格境內發生了一起天災。這是長久以來謝拉格未曾發生的事。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐慌情緒正在蔓延，謝拉格的一切新事物都很容易挑動民眾敏感的神經……你們應該明白我的意思。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信諾希斯先生不會是“神經敏感”的其中之一，對嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，或者說喀蘭貿易對這件事的看法並不重要。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重要的是，人們在等待一個解釋。我也希望能夠和各位一起查明這起天災背後的成因。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那諾希斯先生恐怕要失望了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛檢查過觀測站的各項觀測資料，在天災發生前的七十二小時內，沒有任何一項數值出現異常。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，這片土地上發生了千年來都未曾發生過的天災，但是觀測站沒有檢測到任何有關的異常？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，僅從觀測資料來看，這就是事實。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係的，既然諾希斯先生想要問，那就說清楚好了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "建立在此處的觀測站，主要目的在於觀測研究“星莢”，而非其他。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據現有的研究成果，沒有任何發現指向星莢與天災之間有絲毫關聯。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同樣，如果有人認為建立在此處的觀測站會為謝拉格帶來天災，那更是缺少論證的、主觀性的臆測。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（等……等一下！埃琳娜，這種時候不能再吵架了啦！）", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我接下來要說的話可能有些失禮。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……不用顧慮，請說吧。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少女的聲音平穩，目光堅定，不見轉移。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我不妨把話說得再明白一點吧。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管有違謝拉格基於信仰的認知，但是從科學常理來看，所謂“忽如其來”的天災並不能算是異常。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝拉格長久的平靜，以及把這種平靜當作理所當然的態度，才是一種“異常”。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的前廳內安靜得落針可聞，長走廊的另一頭隱約傳來埃琳娜話語的回音。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在觀測站建立之初，萊茵生命曾經考慮過加入天災預警功能的模組。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但很遺憾，出於對過往經驗的輕信，我們將此模組建立的優先順序往後調整了。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#17$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果說還有什麼補救措施的話……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊茵生命與喀蘭貿易雙方應當重新協商，儘快在謝拉格境內建設完備的天災預警系統——這才是當務之急。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "精彩的見地，這位能量科的……埃琳娜小姐。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我完全認同你的見解，喀蘭貿易會儘快開始準備建立天災預警系統。", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，喀蘭貿易希望複製一份觀測站近一個月來的觀測資料作為留存……方便配合嗎？", "name": "諾希斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_206_gnosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……當然。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請稍等，諾希斯先生。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g5_rhinelab_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#4$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從來都不知道，原來埃琳娜還有這樣的一面啊。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉……繆爾賽思主任，我剛才，是不是太衝動了……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……應該有那麼一點？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是有點生氣，為什麼不管在什麼地方，總是會出現科學要為完全非科學的認知做解釋的情況……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但有些時候，科學距離民眾就是非常遙遠的。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們困擾的這些人和事，其實也是這片大地的一部分，我們不該視而不見。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "用赫默常說的那句話，“科學應該真切地看向每一個人”，對吧？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#2$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白……可是這真的很荒唐——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……先不說了，還是先把需要的資料整理好吧。", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#9$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "資料、資料……就算整理出來也不會有什麼意外的……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等……這一張圖——", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜將散落得到處都是的稿紙整理好，密密麻麻的波譜圖上，一小段曲線引起了她的注意。"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不可能……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這台觀測儀，是用高能粒子束持續轟擊星莢，透過收集電磁輻射來研究星莢的結構……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我剛剛才發現，12月7日凌晨三點到四點之間的數據，與4日同一時間的數據，是完全一樣的……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是很特殊的巧合？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……應該說，是絕對不可能發生的事。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像自然界中不可能找到兩片一模一樣的雪花，大氣中的電磁輻射每分每秒都在發生變化……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是不同的兩天之中的同一時段，整整一個小時內都顯示一模一樣的波段，只有一種可能……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一段數據，被人修改過。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "透過偽造數據來驗證假設？但就算想要學術造假，這也應該是到計劃後期才會做的事……", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能想到有誰會這麼做嗎？", "name": "繆爾賽思"}, "figure_art": "avg_249_mlyss_1#8$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "12月7日……天災發生的前一天……", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_1047_halo2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "67_G3_rhineobservatory_i", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.7, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "